Task 1: Application Configuration

Install Node.js and npm if you haven't already.
Open your terminal and run the following command to install Vite globally:

npm install -g create-vite

Create a new React application with TypeScript using Vite:

create-vite your-app-name --template react-ts

Navigate to your project directory:

cd your-app-name

Install Material-UI (MUI) using npm:

npm install @mui/material @mui/icons-material
